College Athletics
Basketball
lead_paragraph: Tulyah Gaines made two free throws with 16.5 seconds remaining after Notre Dame’s Charel Allen made a key basket and set up another, and the Fighting Irish rallied for a 62-59 victory against California yesterday in Pittsburgh.
